 />\n到時候你就做英雄<br />\n<br />\n唔使再做鍵盤毒撚</blockquote>所以我上黎講，我上黎討論呢個案件<br />\n<br />\n我英唔英勇，我係咪毒撚，唔須要係到討論<br />\n<br />\n如果下下乜都話 人地點關你撚事，咁可以乜都唔討論<br />\n<br />\n上黎討論就係咩都講</blockquote><br />\n但係塊地唔係你既<br />\n<br />\n真係關你撚事咩？<br />\n<br />\n你想保護塊地你就買起塊地慢慢保囉<br />\n<br />\n去買啦"},{"pid":"022d77dbe85c73bf120b9ea525d5cebaae3b659f","tid":605903,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3dfa80b17a44c862be4116819dd569e425b2602","tid":605903,"uid":106276,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:43:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚再回條垃圾屈機男啦 <br />\n條垃圾attention seeker無人理就自覺收皮㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"a2130682206dd8a0f1ef4ea155253c7e3fc151d6","tid":605903,"uid":146707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 我唔係屈機男 )"},{"pid":"3ca54e74e3bcf57108619df015a1364e5600e4b4","tid":605903,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"你班撚樣上網鳩up但做左d乜？<br />\n<br />\n你班鍵盤毒撚有無份去訓？<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鐘意保育一係你班撚樣自己買起塊地<br />\n<br />\n到時塊地係你既就你話事做保育點撚樣都得<br />\n<br />\n事實上你地口中鳩叫正義但實際你做撚過d乜？<br />\n<br />\n鳩叫一陣然後就去打J感覺良好"},{"pid":"b60f22ab4a43e4e829e7004c396d380fdceff101","tid":605903,"uid":125646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"022d77dbe85c73bf120b9ea525d5cebaae3b659f","tid":605903,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3dfa80b17a44c862be4116819dd569e425b2602","tid":605903,"uid":106276,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:43:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚再回條垃圾屈機男啦 <br />\n條垃圾attention seeker無人理就自覺收皮㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-