疲於奔命到處救火。消息稱，上址現多條火龍，消防將火救熄後進行調查，發現火勢蔓延速度不尋常，不排除火警有可疑，交予警方跟進。警方表示，上述兩宗案件合併暫列「縱火」，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。事件中無需疏散，無人受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n如果你仍然覺得火災唔係人為，我會覺得你個人相當無恥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/142222_b81d3ab27ee60ba0b58aa7f9c5664f67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F142222_b81d3ab27ee60ba0b58aa7f9c5664f67.png&h=305d9277&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔尋常 = 100%人為？<br />\n<br />\n你咁英勇<br />\n<br />\n我建議你起南生圍守住<br />\n<br />\n你可以捉放火既凶徒<br />\n<br />\n到時候你就做英雄<br />\n<br />\n唔使再做鍵盤毒撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"唔尋常即係有可疑，即係有機會係人為<br />\n<br />\n定係你想話只係&ldquo;意外&rdquo;？咁卡碧都只係意外"},{"pid":"07003c40399ccad35e294a51bb00d7ab706ea1a0","tid":605903,"uid":123587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"成班傻西係到博見報<br />\n真係有心捉兇就搵航拍機監視啦"},{"pid":"cdb87f11e99c79be36c6ee34dcea2a5af219b3eb","tid":605903,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07003c40399ccad35e294a51bb00d7ab706ea1a0","tid":605903,"uid":123587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"成班傻西係到博見報<br />\n真係有心捉兇就搵航拍機監視啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"警方無消息，民間自己搞，起碼令多d人知，<br />\n<br />\n搏唔搏見報就睇唔透"},{"pid":"910cd04d2a92960ae0588d983ef46511320871e0","tid":605903,"uid":2394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"係人都知邊個係幕後黑手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府會做嘢 嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef3d23cc84cdc4ca1edd629e4b48a282a15762b","tid":605903,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:42